text: Hey guys, it's Rosanna Pansino, I have a geeky baking show online called Nerdy Nummies.
A bunch of my fans online told me about a song called dessert that Dawin made,
and they told me I had to go check him out, so I did.
I went to his channel, I listened to the song and I loved it!
And I listened to it all day, and I was rocking out to it and I said he's pretty cool,
pretty talented! And I had my people get in touch with his people and I said
hey I just think you're really cool, wanna do something?
So he actually came on my baking show the other week, and then he said hey, want to come be in
a music video for it? And I said of course I do! That would be amazing!
